	<name>Retro Sprite Editor</name>
	<developer_name>Dmitrii Naidolinskii</developer_name>
	<summary>The pixel editor for retro consoles.</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>The drawing tool for retro consoles.</p>
		<p>Features for NES: </p> 
		<p>Multiscreen for saving background and load via assembler code.</p>
		<p>Button pencil for drawing pixels. Button mov for moving tiles. Button swap for exchange tiles each other.</p>
		<p>Two banks memory.</p>
		<p>Four palettes for each bank.</p>

		<p>Available platforms: NES</p>
	</description>
